Get Account Balance
get
https://plural-uat.v2.pinepg.in/payouts/v3/payments/funding-account

Use this API to fetch the account balance linked to Pine Labs Online account.

Environment
Use our UAT environment endpoint for testing and for integration utilize our production endpoint.

Environment	Endpoints
User Acceptance Testing [UAT]	https://plural-uat.v2.pinepg.in/payouts/v3/payments/funding-account
Production [PROD]	https://api.pluralpay.in/payouts/v3/payments/funding-account
📘
Note:

You can use this API only when you have a funding account linked to the Pine Labs Online account.
